<h1>NC A&amp;T Experiential Journey Map</h1>
<p class="subtitle"><b>Major Program Content Form</b></p>
<p class="subtitle">Including Concentrations &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; POST TO SHAREPOINT</p>
<p class="tagline">Link Goes Here</p>

<div class="purpose-box">
<b>PURPOSE:</b> This form gathers the content needed to build your department's Experiential Major Map — a two-page visual tool that connects students to academic milestones, experiential learning, and career pathways across all four years. Your input is critical. Please be as specific as possible. If a field does not apply to your program, simply write 'N/A.'
</div>

